# NLPkit

A tiny toolkit that wraps several **scikit-learn** models with
*NLP-aware* preprocessing:

* Tokenisation (NLTK)
* Stop-word removal
* Stemming / lemmatisation
* Contraction expansion
* Auto Count or TF-IDF vectorisation
